DarkMouse::

She ran out of the mess hall and headed for the entrance.  She ran 
outside the base.  She found a small hole in which to crawl into and 
transformed into her mouse mode.  She crawled her way deep into the 
ground and found the empty chamber at the bottom.  There, she curled 
up into a ball and went to sleep.  Over time, her systems shut down 
and she went into self sustained hybernation.  There she would rest 
for eons if nessassary.  One day, she would awaken to find the new 
world.  In her sleep, she dreamed of the predacons ruling the planet 
and winning the beast wars. Bu then, only the matrix new for sure.
